data.description: $5,000 towards closing costs or interest rate buy down. Seller will also provide a home warranty with acceptable offer. Upgrades in this home include the following: new roof 2021 w/ class four shingles, new gutters, drip rail added on roof, side walk around the house, generator plug-in, LED lights in garage, and outdoor gas line for you grilling on the back patio. This beautiful ideal home sitting in Norman is ready for you to come and make it yours! As you step inside, you are greeted by the spacious open living room, kitchen and dining showcasing a masonry fireplace with large windows allowing natural light to flood the space! The kitchen is perfect for the home chef and features new stainless steel appliances, a breakfast bar, granite countertops, and tons of beautiful cabinetry. Your Primary bedroom is complete with a private en-suite shower, including a walk-in shower, soaking tub, and walk in California closet. This house also has three large rooms, built in office space and a full bath in the front. Relax and enjoy a cozy night in underneath the covered patio. You won't want to miss your chance to call this one "Home"! Schedule your private tour now!
